# ─── AI Provider Configuration ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Only one provider is used at a time. Priority order (highest first):
#   1. Google Gemini    (GOOGLE_API_KEY)
#   2. OpenCode Zen     (OPENAI_COMPATIBLE_*)
#   3. Anthropic Claude (ANTHROPIC_API_KEY)
#   4. Mock (fallback — no key needed, returns canned components)
#
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your chosen provider's values.
# The project runs without any API key — mock mode is used automatically.

# ─── OpenCode Zen (recommended) ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Models: big-pickle (free), claude-haiku-4-5, gpt-5.4-mini, etc.
# Get your key at https://opencode.ai/auth
# OPENAI_COMPATIBLE_API_KEY=
# OPENAI_COMPATIBLE_BASE_URL=https://opencode.ai/zen/v1
# OPENAI_COMPATIBLE_MODEL=big-pickle

# ─── Google Gemini ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# GOOGLE_API_KEY=
# GOOGLE_GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-2.5-flash

# ─── Anthropic Claude ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
